    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.title": "安装运输、存储与拆除",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.toc_title": "安装运输、存储与拆除",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.header_ref": "CH.09 — INSTALLATION / STORAGE / DISPOSAL",
    "content.chapter.10-warranty.title": "品牌与保修信息",
    "content.chapter.10-warranty.toc_title": "品牌与保修信息",
    "content.chapter.10-warranty.header_ref": "CH.10 — WARRANTY",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.text": "为了您的安全，在使用本电器产品前，请阅读本手册中的所有说明，并始终遵守以下安全预防措施：",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.1": "本机仅供家庭使用，请勿用于其他非设计用途。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.2": "请勿让儿童玩耍本机或电源线。儿童、行动不便或认知受限人士应在成年人监督下使用。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.3": "小零件可能造成窒息危险，请勿让儿童接触。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.4": "请勿在高湿高温等环境使用本机，严禁在有易燃易爆气体的环境中使用。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.5": "请确保电源电压与机器铭牌标示一致。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.6": "使用后请切断电源。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.7": "从电源插座上拔出插头时请手握插头拔出，请勿拉扯电源线。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.8": "请勿将主机或电源线浸入水中或其他液体中。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.9": "电源线需要直接插接符合安全规范的电源插座上。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.10": "如发现插头、电源线或主机损坏，请立即停止使用并联系制造商或授权维修点处理，请勿自行拆修。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.11": "电源线请勿悬挂于台面边缘，以免儿童拉扯或意外绊倒。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.12": "禁止在手脚潮湿或未穿鞋的情况下触摸产品电源部件。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.13": "产品所连接的电源需有漏电保护装置。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.14": "插座必须满足当地法规要求，安全法规要求强制进行产品接地。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.15": "清洁、维护或更换部件时，必须切断电源。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.16": "切勿将螺丝刀或其它物体插入散热孔中。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.17": "只有授权技术人员才能进行拆机检查和维修。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.18": "发生火灾时，切勿浇水，请使用二氧化碳灭火器。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.19": "除制造商推荐的方法外，不能使用机械手段或其他方法加速除霜。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.20": "不要损坏制冷剂回路。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.21": "警告：易燃材料，存在发生火灾的风险。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.22": "制冷剂废料需在授权废物处理中心处理，不能靠近火源。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.23": "请勿在本产品中储存含有易燃推进剂的气溶胶罐等爆炸性物质。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.24": "保持所有通风口顺畅，保持产品远离热源或蒸汽装置。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.title": "警告 WARNING",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.section_title": "安全须知",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page2.block.1.item.1": "移动或运输产品时保持产品直立，否则可能导致产品损坏。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page2.block.1.item.2": "运输后需静置4小时，待冷媒稳定后再通电。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page2.block.1.item.3": "对电机和制冷系统进行维护时要戴手套。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page2.block.1.item.4": "切勿阻塞散热孔，以确保产品的良好运转。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page2.block.1.item.5": "请勿将非食品类物品放置于腔体中。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page2.block.1.item.6": "本产品仅限室内使用。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page2.block.1.item.7": "本产品设计为将饮用水制作成冰，请不要将本产品用于设计外用途。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page2.block.1.title": "注意 CAUTION",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page2.block.2.item.1": "产品噪音等级低于50 dB(A)。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page2.block.2.item.2": "本产品的气候类型为SN，适合在10℃~32℃ / 50℉~89.6℉ 的环境温度中使用。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page2.block.2.title": "提示 NOTICE",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page2.section_title": "安全须知（续）",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.text": "放置与首次使用",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.2.item.1": "将产品放置在坚固、平坦、干燥的台面上。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.2.item.2": "确保产品四周留有至少 120mm（4.7\"）的通风间距。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.2.item.3": "远离热源（烤箱、灶台等），避免阳光直射。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.2.item.4": "首次使用前，请先运行一次清洁程序（参见 CH.08 维护保养）。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.2.item.5": "首次制冰前 5 次属于水降温阶段，冰形会随水温下降逐渐增大，属正常现象。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.3.text": "用水要求",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.4.item.1": "使用饮用水即可制冰，饮用水越纯净则冰越透明。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.4.item.2": "若想达到理想透明度，请使用矿物质含量较低的饮用水（TDS < 200mg/L）。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.4.item.3": "适用水源：纯净饮用水、RO反渗透处理自来水、深度过滤自来水、低TDS矿泉水。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.4.item.4": "**禁止**使用有色、有味、有气泡或含过饱和气体的饮品（茶、果汁、咖啡、牛奶、汽水等），这些会污染甚至损坏产品。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.5.text": "使用提示",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.6.item.1": "开箱后取出全部包装材料，并用湿布擦拭产品内部后再擦干。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.6.item.2": "子弹冰篮装满后，产品会自动暂停制冰并发出提示音。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.6.item.3": "三种尺寸不能同时制作，但可在制冰途中切换另一种尺寸。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.6.item.4": "连续制冰过程中，受水质、水温和环境温度影响，偶尔出现冰块不透明属正常现象。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.section_title": "产品及使用提示",
    "content.chapter.03-structure.page.page1.section_title": "产品结构",
    "content.chapter.04-features.page.page1.section_title": "产品功能",
    "content.chapter.05-specifications.page.page1.section_title": "技术参数",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.1.text": "工作前准备",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.2.item.1": "务必将产品放置在平整稳固的平面，且产品背部和右侧散热孔处不能放置任何东西，以免阻挡散热。产品与墙或物品之间距离必须 ≥ 120 mm（4.7 in），以确保通风良好。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.2.item.2": "若第一次使用产品，或距离上一次很长时间没有使用产品，请先运行一次清洁程序。请参阅 CH.08 维护保养中的清洁说明。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.3.text": "产品开机",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.4.item.1": "给产品接通电源，产品发出“滴”一声，所有按键点亮后再熄灭，表示已经接通电源。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.4.item.2": "然后点击 **Power** 按键，按键显示白灯，产品已处于开机状态。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.5.text": "如何制作子弹冰",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.6.step.open_lid.text": "打开腔盖，并取出子弹冰篮和水箱。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.6.step.fill_tank.text": "给子弹冰水箱中注满水，注水至水位刻度处。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.6.step.seat_tank.text": "然后将水箱放入子弹冰内腔，请用手按压下水箱，确保已经装到位。水箱松动可能导致产品无法工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.section_title": "操作指引",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.1.step.return_basket.text": "然后放入子弹冰篮，并关闭腔盖。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.1.step.select_size.text": "点击 **Make Ice** 按键，切换点亮按键上方的 S / M / L 指示灯，选择需要制作的子弹冰尺寸。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.1.step.start_cycle.text": "选择完尺寸后，产品自动开始制作子弹冰。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.2.item.1.label_before": "ICE FULL →",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.2.item.2.label_before": "ADD WATER →",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.3.item.1": "制冰中途可点击 **Make Ice** 按键切换制冰尺寸。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.3.item.2": "制冰中途可点击 **Power** 按键终止，子弹冰制冰按键灯熄灭，产品停止子弹冰制冰。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.3.item.3": "当产品检测到子弹冰冰篮装满后，**ICE FULL** 警示灯点亮为绿灯，产品停止制冰。待冰融解，或取走后，产品会自动恢复制冰。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.3.item.4": "请留意，制冰期间若 **ADD WATER** 警示灯点亮红灯，产品会停止制冰，请及时给水箱补充水。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.3.title": "提示 NOTICE",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.section_title": "操作指引（续）",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.header.1": "故障现象",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.header.2": "可能原因",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.header.3": "解决方案",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.1.cell.1": "不能开机",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.1.cell.2": "电源未连接或插座无电",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.1.cell.3": "检查电源连接及插座是否正常。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.2.cell.1": "不能排水",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.2.cell.2": "排水胶塞未松开或排水口堵塞",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.2.cell.3": "检查产品底部排水胶塞是否已松开；检查排水口是否堵塞。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.3.cell.1": "不能制冰",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.3.cell.2": "水箱缺水（ADD WATER亮红灯）",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.3.cell.3": "给水箱加水至水位线。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.4.cell.1": "不能制冰",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.4.cell.2": "制冰模具只结霜无法结冰（管道无法抽水）",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.4.cell.3": "加水至水位线，静置半小时后重新启动。观察制冰兜是否有注水，有则表示抽水泵已复位。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.5.cell.1": "制冰中途停止",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.5.cell.2": "冰篮已满（ICE FULL亮绿灯）",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.5.cell.3": "取走冰块或等待冰融解，产品会自动恢复制冰。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.6.cell.1": "制冰中途停止",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.6.cell.2": "水箱缺水（ADD WATER亮红灯）",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.6.cell.3": "及时给水箱补充水，产品会自动恢复制冰。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.7.cell.1": "前5次冰块偏小",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.7.cell.2": "水温较高，处于降温阶段",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.7.cell.3": "属正常现象，冰形会随水温下降逐渐增大，达到标准尺寸。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.8.cell.1": "制冰效果不理想",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.8.cell.2": "通风间距不足或环境温度过高",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.8.cell.3": "确保四周≥120mm间距；将产品移至阴凉通风处。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.9.cell.1": "冰块不透明",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.9.cell.2": "水质矿物质含量高或水温/环温影响",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.9.cell.3": "使用TDS<200mg/L的纯净水；连续制冰偶尔不透明属正常现象。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.2.text": "如果用户不按照本手册操作产品，并对产品造成任何损坏或质量问题，工厂、经销商及品牌商将不承担任何责任。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.2.title": "免责声明 DISCLAIMER",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.section_title": "故障排除",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.1.text": "自动清洁（制冰模具和制冰兜）",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.2.step.step1.text": "给水箱加水至水位线。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.2.step.step2.text": "开机状态下，点击 **Clean** 按键，按键灯亮白灯，产品自动清洁制冰兜和制冰模。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.2.step.step3.text": "清洁完成后，产品自动停止，按键灯熄灭。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.3.text": "排水操作",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.4.step.step1.text": "断开电源，将产品放置到水槽旁。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.4.step.step2.text": "将产品底部的排水孔塞松脱，让内腔的水排干。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.4.step.step3.text": "排水完成后，将排水孔塞回原位。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.6.text": "日常保养",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.7.item.1": "定期用干净的水清洗产品内部，建议**每天使用前清洗一次**。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.7.item.2": "用柔软湿布擦拭产品外壳，请勿使用腐蚀性清洁剂。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.7.item.3": "请遵循自动清洁步骤清洗制冰模具和制冰兜。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.7.item.4": "清洁保养前请拔掉电源，待产品冷却后再进行处理。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.section_title": "维护保养",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.1.text": "包装运输",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.2.item.1": "运输过程中请保持平衡，防止倾翻；产品倾斜角不得大于 45°。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.2.item.2": "移动或运输产品时应保持直立状态，避免损坏压缩机和制冷系统。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.2.item.3": "运输后需静置 4 小时，待冷媒稳定后再通电。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.3.text": "安装",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.4.item.1": "请将产品安装在平整、稳固、干燥的台面上，不得倾斜放置。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.4.item.2": "搬运时不要推拉产品，以避免倾覆或损坏部件。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.4.item.3": "产品四周与墙或物品之间需保持至少 120mm（4.7\"）的间距，以确保通风和可维护性。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.4.item.4": "请远离热源、蒸汽和阳光直射环境。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.5.text": "存储与拆除",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.6.item.1": "长期存放前，请排空水箱和内腔中的水，并完成清洁与擦干。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.6.item.2": "请将产品置于干燥、通风环境中保存，避免重压和潮湿。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.6.item.3": "本产品含电子元件和 R600a 制冷剂，不得与生活垃圾一同丢弃。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.6.item.4": "拆除或报废时，请联系授权回收机构或零售商，按当地法规进行环保处置。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.7.text": "请勿损坏制冷剂回路。若需要报废处理，请交由具备资质的废弃物处理机构回收，以避免对环境和人身安全造成风险。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.7.title": "WEEE / R600a",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.section_title": "安装运输、存储与拆除",
    "content.chapter.10-warranty.page.page1.block.1.text": "感谢您购买 {{brand.display_name}} {{localized.product_name}}。如有任何问题，请通过以下方式联系我们：\n{{brand.support_email}} | {{brand.website}}",
    "content.chapter.10-warranty.page.page1.block.2.text": "品牌商信息",
